{"tid":1658890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"神探，風水佬，係時候停啦。贏左，你想知咩都得","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T01:12:05.000Z","uid":42149,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0d970a2ce4bb3d4d4691c05a5b1c563f43410379","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"大家，我明白呢幾個月大家有好多懷疑係到<br />\n好多解唔到既謎團，而近期女義士又咁多疑點解釋唔到。<br />\n我有幾個問題<br />\n一<br />\n我地呢一刻所有資料都係人地比既唔知第幾手資料<br />\n二<br />\n討論價值係邊，如果呢一刻有人放條全片出黎，個女義士真係自殺，你地都唔會信，我自己都唔會信<br />\n三<br />\n係，風水野，信則有不信則無。但過份討論會令到大家失哂焦點。<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得我地係為咩出黎，點解要辛辛苦苦打到仆街。有手足比人打到半死，有手足死左，有人因為壓力同絕望而輕生。 我地要既係我地自由，公平，有我地份既香港。唔係比啲所謂既收成期撚樣去控制住。唔係比一理為所慾為既狗去維持香港既冶安。<br />\n我地既五大訴求只係完左一樣，仲有四樣。<br />\n而家仲要比左一樣野，但又拎走返你帶面具既自由。<br />\n唔好因為一個po, 而大家都去盲目地討論風水野。<br />\n唔好因為有人貼左一啲資料，而衝哂去做神探。<br />\n<br />\n請記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏左。所有真相都會浮面<br />\n但係輸左，我地唔只冇左真相，仲要輸一世</span></span><br />\n所以，我地要諗辦法贏，唔係諗辦法證明班狗有殺人。<br />\n佢地有冇殺人。我相信有。而唯一可以搵到真相同對得住我地已經逝去既手足，就係贏左呢場仗。<br />\n<br />\n唔該，麻煩大家，focus 返係遊行，行動po<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1018 - 和你拖</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQpfwCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQpfwCN.jpg&h=a60b32c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ftgf4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ftgf4t.jpg&h=94cb02e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8U4vkv9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8U4vkv9.jpg&h=e810f27d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9n6Bf4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9n6Bf4v.jpg&h=140097f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1020 九龍大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yzi77bj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzi77bj.jpg&h=51731eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2AqTRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2AqTRk.jpg&h=c9aaa523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxwJFwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxwJFwm.jpg&h=248fe2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEauA4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEauA4H.jpg&h=c1ffc65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港。時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9abc081776e697e07eaa3da13e01245d9e27c986","tid":1658890,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b3d6d345d361bc44cca16f5fb5289cf1de247df2","tid":1658890,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可唔可以爭爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日美國眾議院通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n你當撚人condom咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過左就唔駛多謝人？<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n條Bill 未過參議院架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n唔該去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n然後講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#hongkonghumanri