"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"又想人唔去查？ 依家唔查 以後一定石沉大海"},{"pid":"dd31050146aa038cf88bc178187bf2a8d218416f","tid":1658890,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"先攻城 後查案"},{"pid":"fd15636fe4d1276c021e234504b2330385ceb297","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1d785757a1c3de526bdbe24862a7ba3452d6ea6","tid":1658890,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"又想人唔去查？ 依家唔查 以後一定石沉大海"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"你而家查到之後點，你有冇呢單野出現，大部份人都覺得狗係有殺人，唔係唔會冇啦啦咁多浮屍同冇血跳樓案。<br />\n只係當越多人去查件事，個個都掛住查案，忘記左好多野，推行動po, 推遊行，策劃活動。<br />\n<br />\n我地只要贏左運動，解散警隊，我地有真獨立調查<br />\n到時。我地可以知哂全部真相。唔只呢位女義士，係全部人。"},{"pid":"1d40920c386c58df39376ec47fd68f95300052d9","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"香港人。反抗"},{"pid":"82d4834242464be9e38de8ed2fc0731dc3208896","tid":1658890,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"休息幾日又會有新鮮料爆 而加柒婆對準曬連登仔胃口 成個局我地係開手牌玩嘅 非常不利 對面面個浸就不停扮傻畀你地笑"},{"pid":"71cece03a8d900ff2122f7e6c925b4ac50199e02","tid":1658890,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:28.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"da2d6c7adb9b5ca6a60fe6d5b097cc3647d73930","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14a16db02f3e9f8e93b13c1465a402422624de08","tid":1658890,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"f071c6dfda8376bc12940cc5893ded38b65f42ac","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d4834242464be9e38de8ed2fc0731dc3208896","tid":1658890,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"