n><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQpfwCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQpfwCN.jpg&h=a60b32c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ftgf4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ftgf4t.jpg&h=94cb02e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8U4vkv9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8U4vkv9.jpg&h=e810f27d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9n6Bf4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9n6Bf4v.jpg&h=140097f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1020 九龍大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yzi77bj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzi77bj.jpg&h=51731eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2AqTRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2AqTRk.jpg&h=c9aaa523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxwJFwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxwJFwm.jpg&h=248fe2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEauA4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEauA4H.jpg&h=c1ffc65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港。時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"推！加油呀"},{"pid":"17d00150ef0c1221084d89f914c88d4ba60304fa","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d39b2cb68efed869cc3a5c398f2cac3626b7cbee","tid":1658890,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n1020<br />\n和理非，今晚有野做丫"},{"pid":"5116f4efdb7a53986a455e5b55fa898a1bd42c88","tid":1658890,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit